<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nuevo Producto</title>

```
<style>
    *{
        margin:0;
        padding:0;
        box-sizing:border-box;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    body{
        background:#f4f6f9;
        min-height:100vh;
        display:flex;
        justify-content:center;
        align-items:center;
        padding:2rem;
    }

    .container{
        background:white;
        width:100%;
        max-width:600px;
        padding:2rem;
        border-radius:16px;
        box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
    }

    h1{
        text-align:center;
        margin-bottom:2rem;
        color:#1f2937;
    }

    .form-group{
        margin-bottom:1.2rem;
    }

    label{
        display:block;
        margin-bottom:.4rem;
        font-weight:bold;
        color:#374151;
    }

    input,
    select{
        width:100%;
        padding:.8rem;
        border:1px solid #d1d5db;
        border-radius:8px;
        font-size:1rem;
    }

    input:focus,
    select:focus{
        outline:none;
        border-color:#2563eb;
    }

    .btn{
        width:100%;
        border:none;
        background:#2563eb;
        color:white;
        padding:1rem;
        border-radius:8px;
        font-size:1rem;
        cursor:pointer;
        transition:.2s;
    }

    .btn:hover{
        background:#1d4ed8;
    }

    .back-link{
        display:block;
        text-align:center;
        margin-top:1rem;
        text-decoration:none;
        color:#2563eb;
    }

    .back-link:hover{
        text-decoration:underline;
    }
</style>
```

</head>
<body>

```
<div class="container">

    <h1>Registrar Producto</h1>

    <form action="/products/new" method="POST">

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="nombre">
                Nombre del producto
            </label>

            <input
                type="text"
                id="nombre"
                name="nombre"
                placeholder="Ej: Equipación Real Madrid"
                required
            >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="precio">
                Precio
            </label>

            <input
                type="number"
                step="0.01"
                id="precio"
                name="precio"
                placeholder="Ej: 120"
                required
            >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="category_id">
                Categoría
            </label>

            <select
                name="category_id"
                id="category_id"
                required
            >
                <option value="">
                    Seleccione una categoría
                </option>

                <option value="1" name="category_id">
                    Equipaciones
                </option>

                <option value="2" name="category_id">
                    Guayos
                </option>

                <option value="3" name="category_id">
                    Balones
                </option>

            </select>
        </div>

        <button class="btn" type="submit">
            Guardar Producto
        </button>

    </form>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">
        ← Volver al inventario
    </a>

</div>
```

</body>
</html>
